---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <BaseHead />
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <Header />

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Our History</h1>
            <h2>From Passion to the Largest Strength Sports Association</h2>
        </div>
    </section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<main>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title centered-title">The Spartacus Journey</h2>
            <p class="text-center mb-40">Since our founding in 2012, T.S.K.V. Spartacus has grown from a small group of passionate lifters to one of the leading student strength sports associations in the Netherlands.</p>

            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>2011: The Concept</h3>
                        <p>Two friends at Tilburg University came up with the idea of combining strength sports with social activities. After conducting "market research" and finding significant interest, they began planning what would become Spartacus.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>2012: Official Foundation</h3>
                        <p>TSSV Spartacus was officially established on April 11th with the first board consisting of Sjoerd van der Zee (chairman), Jeroen de Beer (secretary), and Tijn Schraa (treasurer).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>2013-2014: Organization Growth</h3>
                        <p>A new logo was introduced that is still used today. Committees were established to distribute workload and increase member involvement, creating the foundation for a more active and sustainable association.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>2014: Competitive Development</h3>
                        <p>Spartacus joined the KNKF (Koninklijke Nederlandse Krachtsport en Fitness Federatie) to promote competitive sports. The association began hosting its own powerlifting competitions, including the DRC Open Powerlifting cup and Dutch national championships.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>2015: Expanding Horizons</h3>
                        <p>Started selling Spartacus gym wear through a collaboration with Wilkin Sports. Changed name from TSSV to TSKV Spartacus to emphasize strength sports. Organized the first members weekend to Antwerp, establishing what would become a yearly tradition.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>2017: Professional Coaching</h3>
                        <p>Powerlifting champion Pjotr van den Hoek joined as the head powerlifting coach under employment of Tilburg University, elevating the training quality for competitive lifters.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>2018: Brand Development</h3>
                        <p>Switched merchandise provider to Tigerprint Merchandise to improve the quality and availability of Spartacus branded gym wear.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>2019: Facility Improvements</h3>
                        <p>Advised the Sports Center management on purchasing new training equipment. The construction committee also became responsible for building the deadlift platforms in the gym.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>2020: Internationalization</h3>
                        <p>All formal events were switched to English to accommodate the growing number of international students at Tilburg University, making the association more inclusive and diverse.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3>Today: Looking Forward</h3>
                        <p>Today, T.S.K.V. Spartacus continues to grow and evolve, providing the latest information, practical know-how, and most importantly, a tight-knit community of gym enthusiasts for all in need of gains!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Testimonials -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title centered-title">Words from Our Founders</h2>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="placeholder-founder.jpg" alt="Spartacus Founder">
                </div>
                <div class="about-text">
                    <blockquote>
                        "Het maakt mij ongelooflijk trots om te zien dat Spartacus zoveel jaar later nog steeds een positieve impact heeft op haar leden. In de beginjaren stond de vereniging nog een beetje apart. Maar door de vastberadenheid en passie van onze leden en besturen, is Spartacus door de jaren heen uitgegroeid tot een onmisbaar onderdeel van het studentenleven in Tilburg. De verenging heeft mij zeer dierbare herinneringen, vriendschappen en ervaringen gegeven die ik al die jaren later nog steeds koester!"
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="text-right"> - Sjoerd van der Zee, Founding Member, T.S.K.V. Spartacus</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <section class="section text-center">
            <h2 class="section-title centered-title">Be Part of Our Future</h2>
            <p class="mb-40">Join T.S.K.V. Spartacus today and become part of our continuing history. Your journey with us starts now!</p>
            <a href="/become-a-member" class="btn">Become a Member</a>
        </section>
    </div>
</main>

    <!-- Footer -->
<Footer />

<script is:inline src="/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
